                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18210411-53-off323 t18210411-53-crimeloc327"></join>. On the 26th of February, about eight o'clock in the evening, my hat laid within three or four feet of the door. My boy called me down stairs - I heard a cry of Stop thief! - I found the prisoner in custody, with it in his hand.</p>
               <p>
            
